# Dependencies & build output (rebuilt inside the image)
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/out
**/coverage

# Secrets — NEVER copy any env file into the build context/image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.production.example

# VCS & tooling
.git
.gitignore
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.log

# OS junk
**/.DS_Store

# Tests & docs not needed at runtime
**/__tests__
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts

# Local certs/keys
**/*.pem
